@startuml
title Communication Diagram - UC007 Đăng xuất

allow_mixing
actor "User" as Actor
boundary "SettingsUI" as UI
control "AuthController" as Controller
entity "SessionManager" as SessionDB

Actor -right-> UI : 1: Bấm Đăng xuất
UI -right-> Controller : 2: logout(token)
Controller -down-> SessionDB : 3: revokeToken()
Controller -up-> UI : 4: Redirect
@enduml